snippet.title: Thomas and the Magic Railroad Print Studio - 2022 Gameplay
snippet.description:
You guys may have seen my post of running Thomas and the Magic Railroad Print Studio on a virtual machine running Windows 98 Second Edition, so I thought to show some gameplay of it! Hope you enjoy!

Thomas & Friends is owned by HiT Entertainment/Mattel.
